BORIS: All right.

01:01:35.890 --> 01:01:37.250
That's all the questions.

01:01:37.250 --> 01:01:41.880
So please join me
in thanking him.

01:01:41.880 --> 01:01:43.380
DALE ANDERSON: Thank you.

01:01:43.380 --> 01:01:45.230
Thank you.

